typeSystemDescription.name: U_compareTypeSystem
typeSystemDescription.description: A sharable and comparable type system for the U-Compare compatible UIMA components.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.DiscontinuousAnnotation
typeDescription.description: Base abstract type for annotations with discontinuous regions.

featureDescription.name: fragments
featureDescription.description: fragments of discontinous region

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.BaseAnnotation
typeDescription.description: Base abstract type for annotations with AnnotationMetadata.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.AnnotationMetadata
typeDescription.description: THIS TYPE WILL BE CHANGED TO INHERIT APACHE UIMA ANNOTATIONMETADATA TYPE, WHEN IT RELEASED.

featureDescription.name: confidence
featureDescription.description: Range of confidence value should be between 0.0 (lowest) and 1.0 (highest).

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.syntactic.SyntacticAnnotation
typeDescription.description: Base abstract type for syntactic annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.bracket.release.SBAR
typeDescription.description: Relative clauses and subordinate clauses, including indirect questions

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.bracket.release.SINV
typeDescription.description: Subject-auxiliary inversion in the case of negative inversion, conditional inversion, locative inversion, and some topicalizations

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.bracket.release.SQ
typeDescription.description: Inverted yes/no question, or main clause of a wh-question, following the wh-phrase in SBARQ

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.bracket.release.NX
typeDescription.description: Used within certain complex NPs to mark the head of the NP

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.function.text.TextFunctionLabel
typeDescription.description: Abstract function tag type for text categories.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.function.grammatical.GrammaticalFunctionLabel
typeDescription.description: Abstract function tag type for grammatical functions.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.function.grammatical.NOM
typeDescription.description: non NPs that function as NPs

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.function.grammatical.DTV
typeDescription.description: the dative object in the unshifted form of the double object construction

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.function.semantic.SemanticFunctionLabel
typeDescription.description: Abstract function tag type for semantic roles.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.label.penn.function.semantic.BNF
typeDescription.description: benefactive, the beneficiary of an action

featureDescription.name: namespace
featureDescription.description: External resource namespace

featureDescription.name: ID
featureDescription.description: ID in the external resource namespace

featureDescription.name: surface
featureDescription.description: Surface string in the dictionary which is used to match the string.

featureDescription.name: posString
featureDescription.description: A special field which internally converts object of pos field into String value.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.Structure
typeDescription.description: Abstract type for structural document annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.Text
typeDescription.description: Abstract type for textual document annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.text.TextBody
typeDescription.description: Abstract type for text body annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.text.Heading
typeDescription.description: Abstract type for text heading annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.Fragment
typeDescription.description: Abstract type for fragmental document annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.DocumentAnnotation
typeDescription.description: Base abstract type for document annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.DocumentClassAnnotation
typeDescription.description: Assumed to be used to express an instance of a document tag.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.DocumentAttribute
typeDescription.description: Abstract type for document attributes, which appear in the document tags.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.DocumentValueAttribute
typeDescription.description: Assumed to be used to correspond to an attribute name-value pair (CDATA in case of DTD).

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.document.DocumentReferenceAttribute
typeDescription.description: Assumed to be used to correspond to an attribute name-id pair (IDREF in case of DTD).

featureDescription.name: goldAnnotations
featureDescription.description: A set of "gold" annotations. Should be filled by developers.

featureDescription.name: testAnnotations
featureDescription.description: A set of "test" annotations. Should be filled by developers.

featureDescription.name: matchedAnnotations
featureDescription.description: A set of annotations, which are recoginized as "matched" through comparison of gold and test annotations. Should be filled by developers.

featureDescription.name: goldAnnotationGroup
featureDescription.description: Reference to the original gold AnnotationGroup. Developers should iterate and pick proper annotations from this FSList.

featureDescription.name: testAnnotationGroup
featureDescription.description: Reference to the original test AnnotationGroup. Developers should iterate and pick proper annotations from this FSList.

featureDescription.name: scores
featureDescription.description: A field to store scores for each CAS. This field should have an instance of *ARRAY* which implements get(i) method e.g. StringArray, IntegerArray, FSArray, etc. Evaluator class should be responsible to make consistent order of scores when there is multiple types of scores exist.

featureDescription.name: fields
featureDescription.description: This field is prepared to store any value which might be used in the evaluation process implemented by the developer, especially values needed when calculate the total score over CASes. U-Compare will not use this field.

featureDescription.name: goldLabel
featureDescription.description: U-Compare will show this label along with the assumed gold standard annotation linked from this MatchedPair instance.

featureDescription.name: testLabel
featureDescription.description: U-Compare will show this label along with the assumed test annotation linked from this MatchedPair instance.

featureDescription.name: matchLabel
featureDescription.description: U-Compare will show this label as a explanatory label of this MatchedPair instance.

featureDescription.name: derivingAnnotationGroups
featureDescription.description: List of AnnotationGroups which are used to produce this AnnotationGroup.

featureDescription.name: derivingAnnotationGroupTypes
featureDescription.description: Array of StringArray, where types used in each corresponding deriving annotation group are stored.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.syntactic.Coordinations
typeDescription.description: Contains an array of constituents which are marked as Coordinations. Corresponds to syn="COOD" in the Genia Treebank.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.comparable.TernaryComparisonSet
typeDescription.description: A special comparison set for similarty matches and gold-test-test ternary comparisons.

featureDescription.name: assumedGoldComparisonSet
featureDescription.description: Link to a comparisonSet, which is an evaluation between the real gold standard and the assumed gold annotations.

featureDescription.name: assumedTestComparisonSet
featureDescription.description: Link to a comparisonSet, which is an evaluation between the real gold standard and the assumed test annotations.

featureDescription.name: ternaryMatchedGoldAnnotations
featureDescription.description: Array of annotations which are matched between the real gold standard, assumed gold and assumed test annotations.

typeDescription.name: org.u_compare.shared.FeatureWeights
typeDescription.description: Stores names and weights of features. For system use.
